Package me.hapyl.spigotutils.module.reflect

Class BoundingBox

java.lang.Object
me.hapyl.spigotutils.module.reflect.BoundingBox
public class BoundingBox extends Object
Create a visual bounding box between two points. A bounding box size cannot exceed 48 blocks.

    • show

      public boolean show()
      Draws a bounding box outline between two locations, if isDefined(), does nothing otherwise. Note that this is limited to 48 blocks for each side due to structure block limitation. (duh)
      Returns:
      true if an attempt of drawing was made, or false if size is greater than MAX_DIST or isDefined() is false.
